## Installation

```
python3.11 -m venv venv

source venv/bin/activate

pip install pdm

pip install build

pdm install

python -m build

pip install ~/machina/machina-core-sdk/dist/machina_sdk-0.1.21-py3-none-any.whl --force-reinstall

```


## Publication

pip install twine

twine upload dist/*


## Release a version
```shell
# Help

semantic-release --help

semantic-release version --help

semantic-release changelog --help


# Generate a version

# patch
# 0.2.2
semantic-release version --config releaserc.toml --patch

# minor
# 0.3.0
semantic-release version --config releaserc.toml --minor

# major
# 1.0.0
semantic-release version --config releaserc.toml --major

# prerelease
# 0.2.1-rc.2
semantic-release version --config releaserc.toml --prerelease

# patch as prerelease
# 0.3.1-rc.1
semantic-release version --config releaserc.toml --patch --as-prerelease

# minor as prerelease
# 0.3.0-rc.1
semantic-release version --config releaserc.toml --minor --as-prerelease

# major as prerelease
# 1.0.0-rc.1
semantic-release version --config releaserc.toml --major --as-prerelease

# prerelease
# 0.2.1-rc.2
semantic-release version --config releaserc.toml --prerelease --as-prerelease
```
